{"word":"ἀντιφωνέω","slug":"ἀντιφωνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀντιφωνέω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to sound in answer, reply</i>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to utter in reply</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to reply to, answer</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}